Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.16,0:01:34.66,Title2,,0,0,0,,{\fs42\fad(450,400)\blur6\pos(984,160)}來自異世界的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.16,0:01:37.62,Title2,,0,0,0,,{\fs58\fad(450,0)\blur6\pos(640,625)}— 溫達利亞城 —
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an8}好...無...聊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.58,0:01:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的啦 好悶 好閒 好無聊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}話說到底算什麼啊 這種待遇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}竟然把我這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:02:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}神出鬼沒變幻無常端莊美麗活潑大方的大怪盜「黑尾」抓來扔一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}實在太奇怪了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能不要在說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 你怎麼這麼從容 什麼嘛 只有你被審問了 好狡猾啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真搞不懂你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}家裡顯眼的寶物都被拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嘛 不過等等再拿回來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你這邊的情況呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個對你很重要的寶物沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}系統修復完成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}機能 正常...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個盒子到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:04:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天也看上去很好吃的樣子~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請盡情享用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我開動了~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恩？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我說這個是里克做的麵包吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恩 怎麼這麼問呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 這個...那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}里克在哪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是去外送麵包了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我沒拜託過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拜託過里克去外送了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦！ 我不清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}歡迎光臨！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}輝夜來過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不在診所裡頭說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦！什麼時候發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去房間看了一下 就發現不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我去找她看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:06:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不用不用 已經讓伊莉雅去找了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}應該不會有什麼事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉了 如果看到輝夜的話 能把她帶到診所來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果需要幫忙的話請儘管開口哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恩 謝謝大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}里克還沒回來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說不定在找輝夜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的也是呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:07:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}尋找的時候迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吶 輝夜可能已經自己回到診所了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}里克可能也在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等收拾好了去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到來的太快了呀...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已經變成紅月了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍著點啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬上就帶你去診所...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}傷員？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喲 又見面了呢 年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}迪蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}究竟發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就像你看到的這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是在海上被解決了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}變成這種慘樣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被解決了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊... 巨大的武裝船隊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}武裝船隊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這艘船完全沒辦法和它相比
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且還向著這座島前進
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有話等等再說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}裡面還有傷員
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幫我把醫生叫過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊... 還有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幫我帶瓶頂級的朗姆酒來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}報告！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}從擱淺船的船員口中得知
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在海上遭遇的武裝船隊 有好幾艘護衛艦和巨大的本艦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}目標應該是溫達利亞島
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}報告完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這件事鎮上的人都已經...？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為傷員的救助交給了普通市民
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早晚會有傳開的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒辦法了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請退下！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.26,0:10:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呀！ 怎...怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是皇后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個女孩是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是輝夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一直在診所裡昏迷的...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼來這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為從異世界來的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}異世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}世界就像交錯在一起一樣 存在著無數的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}平時絕不會相會 從這一點開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:11:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感受到了時光空間中的些微搖盪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也就是說相會了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}機械人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你也不是這個世界的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不否認
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要保護主人免受危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個世界搖晃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}主人什麼的...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}保護我？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}主人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}擁有強大力量的大船隊準備強行把你從這個世界帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這座城堡遠離海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被小鎮和城牆所保護著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被認定為是小島上最安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果藏在這裡的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我如果沒被找到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那船隊的人會...？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}排除所有障礙 不管怎麼樣都要找到你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}排除算什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在島上隨意破壞嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別這麼冷靜的說出這種事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的準備利用這座島嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}相對的 可以想辦法製造出反擊的時機
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}保護我？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}會被帶走？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你也該睡一下了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能好的傷也好不了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在怎麼會睡得著啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:13:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快給我帶瓶好酒過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行 受傷時候就忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}完全不聽的我話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呃...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行 酒的話還是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊... 每個人都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有 還沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}里克? 里克的話現在還在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}里克！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喲... 呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喲什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到現在為止你是跑去哪啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就這麼消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,0:13:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家都很擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呃...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈哈哈...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓女孩子擔心可不行啊 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不需要要對這種人道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你難道認為沒人擔心你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個... 迪蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:13:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恩？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.81,0:14:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在海上交戰的那個武裝船隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是怎麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他們在那距離溫達利亞一天的海上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然有做的過火的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對方也沒有原諒過我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一下子彈藥就用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蛇或蜥蜴之纇的怪物 就跑到船上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}它們不是這個世界的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也就是說他們向著這裡來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}教會的孩子們肯定都在害怕著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事的 拉格納斯大人和露菲娜大人肯定會想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 但是這種時候輝夜不見了...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}果然發生了什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呃...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}輝夜？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}里克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們去找輝夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Yeah~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怪盜黑尾撤退~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這段台詞不說也無所謂吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣的事情... 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣的話 診所和麵包店被破壞了...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}島上的大家...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這種事絕對不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果我去大家能得救的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 你在說什麼漂亮話啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}瞭解了 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個是主人最信賴的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喵~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 就算這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被這麼關著我也...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬上就要外面了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就這樣分頭找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}隨著時間流逝 世界交融了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以及地下之中...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}外面的知情者如同自己所嚮往的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和這個世界相連的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:17:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喵~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一直是紅月當空
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}紅月是晚上的自豪之日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}世界崩壞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}互相瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太棒了~！ 撤退大成功~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這種事不會讓你們得逞的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}噢！~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好幾次粗心被你們逃掉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這可受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:18:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能告訴我到底發生了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還是說是關於這個精靈石的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}輝夜...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就只剩亞蜜露了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:20:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}肯定會找到輝夜一起回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東面能想到的地方都找過了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}亞蜜露不需要道歉的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為努力找過了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的啊 到底在哪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果就像這樣無法在見面的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不會有這種事的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在肯定還在哪裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}確認了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}船隊還在接近中！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聯絡城堡 趕緊準備炮擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}武裝船隊...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.05,0:21:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.38,0:23:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}輝夜好像和機械人偶一起去了海盜船那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.47,0:23:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}我們現在到底應該做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.51,0:23:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}為了下次也能做出幸福的麵包！
